Thank you for all of your support thus far since the beginning when we introduced our Kinder Learning/Busy Boxes! We are so glad that all of your little ones are having fun with the activities and learning at the same time 🤗 We'd like to thank your support by holding this giveaway and we will be giving away ONE Kinder Busy Box V2! ✨ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
To enter this giveaway:
1) Like this post
2) Follow @dekinderclubsg on Instagram & Facebook
3) Tag 3 friends with kids 0 - 6 years old (one comment/entry)
4) Multiple entries allowed
5) Share this post on your igstory & tag us! (make sure your profile is public)
6) BONUS: Ensure your friends are following us on our social media platforms too! ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Giveaway ends 31st May 2020, Sunday, 11:59PM! ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
